item.title: Anyone down for a DnB mega collab?
item.dc:creator: El1011
item.description:
El1011:

Im on the 5.0 still due to storage issues on my phone

my phone literally only has megabytes of storage left. i cant even take a picture on my phone anymore. Another issue is that if i update to V6, my project files are no longer stored on the cloud rather instead they’re local now, so that’s more storage that i dont have. Also i’m hoping to get a new phone sometime soon (the 11 pro is looking pretty promising), so i’d lose all my projects because they’re stored locally.
Since mine are still backing up to icloud, i could get a new device and just pull them down instead of having to export every project and re open the links on said new device.

item.title: Anyone down for a DnB mega collab?
item.dc:creator: El1011
item.description:
was it for one of the auxy collective collabs?
i was involved with 2 of those. it worked before when the only issue was the subscription, but im not on the same version as everyone else. Im on the 5.0 still due to storage issues on my phone and due to non-backwards compatibility with V6, i can’t open newer project files.

what i might be able to do is have someone export the whole project as an ableton set and i can do my part in ableton, but then it’s no longer just an auxy track so…
